:"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would pray at night in cycles two by two, then he used the toothstick after he finished. Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 288 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32970,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/30\/how-recognize-the-ummah\/","url_meta":{"origin":35732,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: How will you recognize Muslims in the Hereafter?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 30, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: It was said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, how will you recognize those you have never seen from your nation?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cRadiant streaks upon their limbs from the traces of ablution.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 284 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33065,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/03\/know-your-best-deed-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":35732,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Know your best deed is the prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cRemain upright, though you cannot encompass it entirely. Know that the most favorable of your deeds is prayer and that none can preserve his ablution but a believer.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 278 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38821,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/18\/punished-qabr-urine\/","url_meta":{"origin":35732,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Tahara: Punishment in grave for uncleanliness with urine","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 18, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cMost of the torment in the grave is due to carelessness with urine.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 348 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0643\u0652\u062b\u064e\u0631\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0630\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32411,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/21\/two-men-punished-in-graves\/","url_meta":{"origin":35732,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Graves: Two men punished for backbiting, uncleanliness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 21, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakrah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, passed by two graves and he said, \u201cVerily, they are both being punished, but not for a sin difficult to avoid. As for one, he is punished for the habit of soiling himself with urine. As for the other,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24459,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/02\/26\/dua-leaving-bathroom\/","url_meta":{"origin":35732,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication for leaving the lavatory","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 26, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would say upon leaving the washroom, \u201cAll praise is due to Allah, who has removed harm from me and granted me wellness.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 301 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\